Guess this returns the favor with castle prophylaxis. Jw could have blocked with 14  Bd2  but after I ... Bxb2 then 15. Qxb2 I would be able to ... Ne5. At that point we would have equality on points, but I would favor my position. Kf1 is not a bad move.
